 taps on the body of the callout view, as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"opposed to the callout’s left or right accessory view. If the annotation has a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom callout view via the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is only called whenever the callout view calls its delegate’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutViewDelegate\/calloutViewTapped:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If this method is present on the delegate, the standard callout view’s body","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"momentarily highlights when the user taps it, whether or not this method does","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"anything in response to the tap.","type":"text"}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts, learn how to trigger an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"action when an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"s "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is tapped."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped on an annotation’s callout view.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:taponcalloutforannotation:"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit